media:group.media:title: Miko fangame combat demo
media:group.media:description:
Showcasing several mechanics including:
- Enemy waves system
- 3 different modes with unique capabilities
- Dashing and focusing
- Parrying melee attacks
- Melee combo damage bonus
- Active item

The passive HP regeneration you might notice here is for debug purposes only, but there will be many different ways to recover HP in the game proper

No boss fights to show yet but that's where the real meat of the game will be, so please look forward to it!

Music is an instrumental remix of LamazeP's Ochame Kinou made specifically for this game
